l]] (1997)\n*[[Renault]] (1899)\n*[[Rimac Automobili|Rimac]] (2009)\n*[[Rinspeed]] (1979)\n*[[w:de:Roding Automobile|Roding]] (2008)\n*[[Roewe]] (2006)\n*[[Rolls-Royce Motor Cars|Rolls-Royce]] (1906)\n*[[Rossin-Bertin]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gtspirit.com/2011/07/12/official-rossin-bertin-vorax/|title=Official: Rossin-Bertin Vorax - Brazilian Supercar - GTspirit|author=Lawrence Adams|work=GTspirit}}</ref> (2011)\n*[[Rossion]] (2008)  \n*[[Ruf Automobile]] (1939)\n{{div col end}}\n\n==S==\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n*[[SAIC-GM-Wuling]] (2002)\n*[[SAIPA]] (1966)\n*[[Saker Cars|Saker]] (1989)\n*[[Saleen]]<ref>http://saleen.com/</ref>\n*[[Renault Samsung Motors|Samsung]] (1994)\n*[[Sbarro (automobile)|Sbarro]] (1971)\n*[[SEAT]] (1950)\n*[[Shanghai Maple]] (2000)\n*[[SIN Cars|SIN]] (2012) <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sincars.co.uk/|title=SIN CARS|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autocar.co.uk/car-news/autosport-international/road-legal-200mph-sin-r1-go-production|title=2015 Sin R1 - prices, specification and pictures|author=Darren Moss|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.motorauthority.com/news/1092972_sin-cars-teases-new-r2-supercar-ahead-of-goodwood|title=Corvette-Powered Sin R1 Road Car Enters Production: Video|author=Viknesh Vijayenthiran|date=14 July 2015|work=Motor Authority}}</ref>\n*[[\u0160koda Auto|\u0160koda]] (1895)\n*[[Smart (automobile)|Smart]] (1994)\n*[[Spada Codatronca|Spada Vetture Sport]] (2008)\n*[[GTA Motor| Spania GTA]] (2005)\n*[[Spyker Cars]] (1999)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nu.nl/economie/3982047/faillissement-spyker-teruggedraaid.html|title=Faillissement Spyker teruggedraaid|trans-title=Bankruptcy Spyker revoked|publisher=NU.nl|date=29 January 2015|accessdate=29 January 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Ssangyong Motor]] (1954)\n*[[SSC North America]] (1999)\n*[[Subaru]] (1953)\n*[[Suzuki]] (1909)\n{{div col end}}\n\n==T==\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n*[[Tanom]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tanommotorsusa.com/|title=Welcome 