o Year 13, having previously hosted only students in Years 7 through 12 during its inaugural academic year (2010/11).<ref name=\"OIS_website\">{{cite web|url=http://www.oeirasinternationalschool.com/|title=Welcome to Oeiras International School - Oeiras International School|website=Oeiras International School}}</ref>\n\nThe school campus is based on the premises of a 17th-century [[palace]],<ref name=\"OIS_website\"/><ref name=\"Camara_Oeiras\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.cm-oeiras.pt/voeiras/GalIma%5CPaginas/Quinta%20Nossa%20Sra.%20Da%20Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o.aspx |title=Archived copy |access-date=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111229083806/http://www.cm-oeiras.pt/voeiras/GalIma/Paginas/Quinta%20Nossa%20Sra.%20Da%20Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o.aspx |archive-date=2011-12-29 |url-status=dead }}</ref> the ''Quinta de Nossa Senhora da Concei\u00e7\u00e3o'' in Barcarena, [[Oeiras Municipality, Portugal|Oeiras]]. The 5 [[hectare]] campus was newly refurbished in 2011, boasting a vast array of state-of-the-art amenities.<ref name=\"OIS_website\"/> During its inaugural year (2010/2011), the school opened at temporary premises, located at ''Fundi\u00e7\u00e3o de Oeiras'',<ref name=\"Boas_Noticias\">{{cite web|url=http://www.boasnoticias.pt/index.aspx?p=MenuDetail&MenuId=1429&ParentId=20|title=P\u00e1gina n\u00e3o encontrada|access-date=2010-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910224644/http://www.boasnoticias.pt/index.aspx?p=MenuDetail&MenuId=1429&ParentId=20|archive-date=2011-09-10|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref name=\"Qualidade_Online\"/><ref name=\"Convergence\"/><ref name=\"Universia\">[http://www.universia.pt/servicos_net/informacao/noticia.jsp?noticia=59968 ]{{dead link|date=July 2018}}</ref> but has since been located at its present campus.<ref name=\"OIS_website\"/>\n\nOIS has ambitious plans to become an tensor [[Eco-Schools|Eco-School]] and intends to promote Environmental Awareness and Social Responsibility with the provision of scholarships and community service.<ref name=\"Qualidade_Online\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.qualidadeonline.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=2122&Itemid=1 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2010-05-29 |archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20100529123425/http://www.qualidadeonline.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=2122&Itemid=1 |archive-date=2010-05-29 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"Convergence\">{{Cite web |url=http://convergence.com.pt/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=452%3A1o-escola-internacional-de-oeiras-abre-em-setembro&catid=42%3Aoff-topic&Itemid=50 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813233055/http://convergence.com.pt/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=452:1o-escola-internacional-de-oeiras-abre-em-setembro&catid=42:off-topic&Itemid=50 |archive-date=2011-08-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nAt a launch event held at Hotel Palacio in Estoril in 2010, the school's Principal described the school saying \"OIS is committed to promoting quality education and values in a changing world, encouraging students to become responsible for their own learning. We will focus on intellectual rigour, helping all students to achieve their full potential\".<ref name=\"Portugal_News\">{{cite web|url=http://www.theportugalnews.com/cgi-bin/article.pl?id=1061-49|title=New International School to open in Oeiras|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n==Motto==\nThe school motto is [[Sapere aude|Sapere Aude]] (Dare to Learn).<ref name=\"OIS_website\"/>\n\n==Location==\nQuinta de Nossa Senhora da Concei\u00e7\u00e3o,\n\u00e0 Rua Antero de Quental,\nBarcarena,\n2780-001 Oeiras,\nPortugal <ref name=\"HotFrog\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hotfrog.pt/Empresas/Oeiras-International-School|title=Oeiras International School, Oeiras Lisboa - Ensino  - Hotfrog Portugal|website=www.hotfrog.pt}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Portugal|Schools}}\n*[[Education in Portugal]]\n*[[Eco-Schools]]\n*[[Afrixalus osorioi]]\n*[[Bulbophyllum xanthophaeum]]\n*[[Rhuma thiobapta]]\n*[[Bittium watsoni]]\n*[[Tippmannia olivascens]]\n*[[Amphicnaeia brevivittis]]\n*[[Hierodoris huia]]\n\n==References==\n<!--- See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Footnotes on how to create references using  tags which will then appear here automatically -->\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.oeirasinternationalschool.com/ Official School Website]\n{{International schools in Portugal}}\n\n[[Category:International schools in Portugal]]<!--not in the Lisbon city limits-->\n[[Category:Education in Oeiras]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Lisbon District]]\n[[Category:International Baccalaureate schools in Portugal]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 2010]]\n[[Category:Education in Lisbon]]\n[[Category:2010 establishments in Portugal]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox school\n| name = Oeiras International School\n| native_name = \n| latin_name = \n| logo = Oeiras International School Logo.jpg\n| seal_image = \n| image = \n| image_size = \n| alt = \n| caption = \n| motto = Sapere Aude\n| motto_translation = Dare to Learn\n| location = Barcarena\n| streetaddress = \n| region = Oeiras\n| city = [[Lisbon]]\n| state = \n| province = \n| county = \n| postcode = \n| postalcode = \n| zipcode = \n| country = [[Portugal]]\n| country1 = \n| coordinates = {{Coord|38|43|36|N|9|16|41|W|source:fiwiki_region:PT_type:edu|display=it}}\n| schooltype = Private IB World School\n| fundingtype = Non-Profit Organisation\n| religious_affiliation = \n| religion = \n| denomination = \n| patron = \n| established = \n| founded = 2010\n| opened = 1 September 2010\n| founder = \n| status = \n| closed = \n| locale = \n| schoolboard = \n| district = \n| LEA = \n| authority = \n| category = \n| category_label = \n| oversight = \n| oversight_label = \n| authorizer = \n| superintendent = \n| trustee = \n| specialist = \n| session = \n| school_number = \n| school_code = \n| MOE = \n| ofsted = \n| ceeb = \n| president = \n